OL,3,CMedway Maritime Hospital A&E 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' due to overcrowding,
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe Medway NHS Trust has been warned
OL,8,Fto make specific improvements to solve
OL,9,Fovercrowding in one of its Kent
OL,10,Fhospitals.
OL,12,FAn inspection by the Care Quality
OL,13,FCommission, in February 2024, looked
OL,14,Finto the care provided by urgent and
OL,15,Femergency services at the Medway
OL,16,FMaritime Hospital in Gillingham.
