OL,3,CMedway Maritime Hospital A&E 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' due to overcrowding,
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt found the overall rating for the
OL,8,Fdepartment has declined from good to
OL,9,Frequires improvement, with the CQC
OL,10,Fissuing a warning notice to focus the
OL,11,Ftrust's attention on making specific
OL,12,Fimprovements to resolve overcrowding.
OL,14,FThe report said people were being
OL,15,Fcared for in undesignated areas, which
OL,16,Fwas impacting on people's privacy and
OL,17,Fdignity.
