OL,3,CMedway Maritime Hospital A&E 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' due to overcrowding,
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe hospital was rated as 'inadequate'
OL,8,Ffor safety, 'requires improvement' for
OL,9,Fbeing effective, responsive & caring.
OL,10,FThe services were rated 'good' for
OL,11,Fbeing well-led.
OL,13,FThe CQC says it will continue to
OL,14,Fmonitor the trust, ensure people are
OL,15,Fsafe whilst these improvements are
OL,16,Fbeing made and will return to check on
OL,17,Ftheir progress.
