OL,3,CMedway Maritime Hospital A&E 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement' due to overcrowding,
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FJayne Black, Chief Executive of Medway
OL,8,FNHS Foundation Trust said: "We are
OL,9,Fvery sorry that despite the best
OL,10,Fefforts of our hard-working staff, at
OL,11,Fthe time of the last February's
OL,12,Finspection the inspection team found
OL,13,Fthat our care fell below the standard
OL,14,Fthat everyone should expect in their
OL,15,Ftime of need.
