OL,4,Cimprovement' due to overcrowding,
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Over the last year we have made
OL,8,Fsignificant improvements so that
OL,9,Fpatients attending our Emergency
OL,10,FDepartment are treated sooner, are
OL,11,Fcared for in areas more suitable for
OL,12,Ftheir needs, and receive appropriate
OL,13,Fand compassionate care.
OL,15,F"We recognise there is much more for
OL,16,Fus to do, particularly to reduce
OL,17,Fdelays for patients waiting to be
OL,18,Fadmitted to a ward, so that every
OL,19,Fpatient receives the high standard of
OL,20,Fcare that we aspire to provide.
